title: "Ep 343: The Mask (1994) 30th Anniversary Recap and Review!"
publishDate: "2024-08-08"
category: "major-issues"
episodeNumber: 343
spotifyUrl: "https://comicbookclique.podbean.com/e/ep-343-the-mask/"
