Hold on to your hats and green face paint, folks as it is time to celebrate the timeless classic The Mask in time for its 30th anniversary! Join us as we rewind to the '90s to celebrate Jim Carrey in all his manic glory, from those wild dance moves to the cartoonish chaos that made us all wish we had our own magical mask. We’ll chat about the film’s bonkers humor, the unforgettable one-liners, and, of course, the love story that somehow fits between all the mayhem. So, tune in for a trip down memory lane that's as wild as a night at the Coco Bongo Club—this episode is s-s-smokin'!" Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by ComicBook Clique, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

 

Send us feedback at ComicBookClique@Gmail.com! You Are Worthy! 

